# Release Checklist

Before considering a new page or major change ready for merge, verify:

## SEO
- [ ] `generateMetadata()` present with title, description, canonical, alternates, og, twitter
- [ ] StructuredData component included
- [ ] Hreflang tags for IT + EN + x-default
- [ ] Slug is lowercase, hyphenated, max 3 words

## Content
- [ ] All copy comes from `messages/it.json` + `messages/en.json`
- [ ] IT and EN JSON keys are in sync
- [ ] No hardcoded strings in TSX
- [ ] Meta description is 150-160 characters
- [ ] Single H1 per page

## Technical
- [ ] No layout shift (images have explicit dimensions)
- [ ] Images below-the-fold are lazy loaded
- [ ] Mobile responsive verified
- [ ] No unnecessary `"use client"` directives

## Routing
- [ ] Slug does not conflict with funnel registry (`src/lib/reserved-slugs.ts`)
- [ ] If new top-level route, added to `RESERVED_SITE_SLUGS`
- [ ] Internal links use `next/link` with locale-aware paths

## Tracking
- [ ] Section view events configured (if applicable)
- [ ] CTA click events configured
- [ ] Conversion events mapped
